OL,3,CRail services grind to standstill as
OL,4,Cpay dispute nears two years
OL,6,FThis latest walkout will end tonight
OL,7,Fbut it could have a knock on effect
OL,8,Ftomorrow and passengers are advised to
OL,9,Fcheck before they travel.
OL,11,FAslef members at 16 train companies
OL,12,Fare also banning overtime on Monday
OL,13,Fand Tuesday which will disrupt
OL,14,Fservices.
OL,16,FThe dispute over pay and working
OL,17,Fconditions between ASLEF and rail
OL,18,Foperators is into its 22nd month, with
OL,19,Fno sign of a breakthrough and no talks
OL,20,Fplanned.
