OL,3,CRail services grind to standstill as
OL,4,Cpay dispute nears two years
OL,6,FA Rail Delivery Group spokesperson
OL,7,Fsaid, "Train companies are working
OL,8,Fthrough plans to manage the
OL,9,Funnecessary disruption to our
OL,10,Fpassengers caused by this damaging
OL,11,Findustrial action."
OL,13,F"In the meantime we remain committed
OL,14,Fto resolving this dispute and our
OL,15,Foffer, which would take average driver
OL,16,Fsalaries to #65,000 for a four-day
OL,17,Fweek without overtime, remains on the
OL,18,Ftable."
