OL,6,FRDG says industrial action since June
OL,7,F2022 has cost the sector around #798
OL,8,Fmillion, stalling its post-pandemic
OL,9,Frecovery and threatenings its long-
OL,10,Fterm sustainability.
OL,12,FThe union says the dispute has cost
OL,13,Fthe industry more than #2 billion,
OL,14,Fmore than it would have cost to
OL,15,Fresolve the conflict.
